rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貴到仆街。舉個例，照x光無保險4k usd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9419d157a920b613b7d0d036f7534d4edf11997","tid":264361,"uid":401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>無旅遊保咩？</blockquote><br />\n有呀</blockquote><br />\n有就唔洗咁擔心，睇妳睇咩囉，感冒發燒大部分可以claim返。不過有d保險公司可能要你墊左先，有d可以直接碌。每個case都有complication，具體數字答唔到你。"},{"pid":"a87d5d3747c921f944fbe6f3e6db78b7c2ee54ea","tid":264361,"uid":2153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:56:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>旅客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇one medical 門診，要幾錢左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貴到仆街。舉個例，照x光無保險4k usd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁屙嘔門診呢"},{"pid":"005c42a3243f7677beda2a909d9ef4f90c3076e4","tid":264361,"uid":401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T17:58:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>旅客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想睇one medical 門診，要幾錢左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n貴到仆街。舉個例，照x光無保險4k usd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁屙嘔門診呢</blockquote><br />\n我建議你去d community clinic睇，唔得就去唐人街搵下。醫院睇預差唔多一千美金咁樣囉。其實唔係太嚴重去drug store買藥食再好好地訓返教就得啦。"},{"pid":"7d4bfa8e736161afcb48a3a0a60fc2eb1f9a4a87","tid":264361,"uid":2153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T18:02:50.000Z","msg":"<blockq